00001612                           772  * Section       : Delta Time
00001612                           773  * Description   : For slowing down runtime, make it consistent.
00001612                           774  *-----------------------------------------------------------
00001612                           775  LAST_TIME       DS.L    1       ; milliseconds elapsed lsat cycle
00001616                           776  CURRENT_TIME    DS.L    1       ; milliseconds passed since last cycle
0000161A                           777  DELTA_TIME      DS.L    1       ; multiply any velocity with this to make movement over time consistent.
